## 4. The Vault Structure

```
YourVault/
│
├── CLAUDE.md                        ← AI agent instructions (see Section 10)
├── VAULT-MANUAL.md                  ← Comprehensive reference (this system's manual)
├── 00-Dashboard.md                  ← Navigation hub, links to everything
│
├── 01-Inbox/
│   ├── Now/                         ← High priority, process within 48 hrs
│   ├── Fleeting/                    ← Quick captures, fragments, half-formed thoughts
│   └── Someday-Maybe/               ← Interesting but not urgent. Review weekly.
│
├── 02-Journal/
│   ├── Daily/                       ← YYYY-MM-DD.md daily logs
│   └── Weekly/                      ← YYYY-Wnn.md weekly reviews
│
├── 03-Projects/
│   └── [ProjectName]/
│       └── 00-Hub.md                ← One hub per project
│
├── 04-Areas/
│   └── [AreaName]/
│       └── [area-name].md           ← One note per area
│
├── 05-Resources/
│   ├── Literature-Notes/            ← Summaries of sources in your own words
│   ├── Slip-Box/                    ← Permanent atomic notes (FLAT, no subfolders)
│   │   └── MOCs/                    ← Maps of Content (thematic indexes)
│   └── Knowledge-Bank/
│       ├── Books/                   ← Book notes
│       ├── People/                  ← Person hubs and contact logs
│       ├── Quotes/                  ← Memorable quotes
│       ├── Vocabulary/              ← Words you're learning
│       └── Raw/                     ← Saved PDFs, links (prefix: pdf-/book-/link-)
│
├── 06-Archive/                      ← Nothing is deleted — moved here instead
│
└── 07-Templates/                    ← All note templates
    ├── daily-journal.md
    ├── weekly-review.md
    ├── project-hub.md
    ├── literature-note.md
    ├── permanent-note.md
    ├── book-note.md
    ├── area-note.md
    ├── quote-note.md
    ├── vocab-note.md
    ├── person-note.md
    └── meeting-note.md
```

**Critical rules for the Slip-Box:**
- Always flat. Never create subfolders inside `05-Resources/Slip-Box/` except `MOCs/`.
- Every permanent note gets a timestamped filename: `YYMMDD-kebab-title.md`
- One idea per note. No exceptions.

