### Step 5 — Create project hubs for your active projects

Use the `project-hub.md` template. Put each project in its own subfolder under `03-Projects/`:
```
03-Projects/
  ProjectName/
    00-Hub.md     ← created from project-hub template
```

### Step 6 — Create area notes for your ongoing responsibilities

Use the `area-note.md` template. Common areas: Health, Finance, Career, a specific course or degree, Relationships, Home.

### Step 7 — Optionally create MOCs for your main topics

A Map of Content (MOC) is an index note. It doesn't contain ideas — it links to permanent notes on a theme. Create `MOC-TopicName.md` in `05-Resources/Slip-Box/MOCs/`.

