## 7. Tag Taxonomy

**Rule: never invent tags outside this list.** A tag system is only useful if it is consistent. The moment you start improvising, the taxonomy collapses.

Tags in YAML frontmatter have **no `#`** symbol. In note body text, use `#tag` inline.

### Status / Maturity
```
seedling   budding   evergreen
```

### Note Types
```
fleeting   literature   permanent   moc   hub
journal    review       book        quote  vocab
person     meeting
```

### Meta (cross-cutting concerns)
```
toprocess   question   insight   idea
```

### Your Research / Work Topics
Create a group of tags for each major domain you work in. Examples:

```
# Domain 1 tags
[tag1]  [tag2]  [tag3]

# Domain 2 tags
[tag4]  [tag5]  [tag6]
```

Keep domain tags specific and consistent. Use noun forms (`quantization`, not `quantized` or `quantizing`).

### Personal Areas
```
health    fitness    sleep    nutrition
finance   expense    savings
habit     reflection career
```

