## 8. Dynamic Views with Obsidian Bases

Obsidian Bases (`.base` files) create live, filterable database views of your notes. They are YAML files. Place them inside the folder they filter.

### `03-Projects/projects-overview.base`
Shows all project hubs with status, deadline, and days since last update.

```yaml
filters:
  - 'type == "hub"'

formulas:
  status_icon: 'if(status == "active", "🟢", if(status == "paused", "🟡", "✅"))'
  days_since_update: '(now() - file.mtime).days.round(0)'

properties:
  formula.status_icon:
    displayName: ""
  formula.days_since_update:
    displayName: "Days since update"
  status:
    displayName: "Status"
  deadline:
    displayName: "Deadline"

views:
  - type: table
    name: "Active Projects"
    filters:
      - 'status == "active"'
    order:
      - formula.status_icon
      - file.name
      - deadline
      - formula.days_since_update
```

---

### `05-Resources/Literature-Notes/literature-tracker.base`
Tracks your reading pipeline by status.

```yaml
filters:
  and:
    - file.inFolder("05-Resources/Literature-Notes")
    - 'file.ext == "md"'

formulas:
  type_icon: 'if(source-type == "paper", "📄", if(source-type == "book", "📚", if(source-type == "video", "🎬", "🌐")))'

properties:
  formula.type_icon:
    displayName: "Type"
  author:
    displayName: "Author"
  year:
    displayName: "Year"
  status:
    displayName: "Status"

views:
  - type: table
    name: "To read"
    filters:
      - 'status == "toread"'
    order:
      - formula.type_icon
      - file.name
      - author
      - year

  - type: table
    name: "In progress"
    filters:
      - 'status == "reading"'
    order:
      - file.name
      - author

  - type: table
    name: "Processed"
    filters:
      - 'status == "processed"'
    order:
      - formula.type_icon
      - file.name
      - author
      - year
```

---

### `05-Resources/Slip-Box/seedlings.base`
Tracks permanent note maturity — shows what needs promotion.

```yaml
filters:
  and:
    - file.inFolder("05-Resources/Slip-Box")
    - 'file.ext == "md"'
    - not:
        - file.inFolder("05-Resources/Slip-Box/MOCs")

formulas:
  days_old: '(now() - file.ctime).days.round(0)'
  maturity_icon: 'if(status == "evergreen", "🌲", if(status == "budding", "🌿", "🌱"))'

properties:
  formula.maturity_icon:
    displayName: ""
  formula.days_old:
    displayName: "Age (days)"
  status:
    displayName: "Maturity"
  source:
    displayName: "Source"

views:
  - type: table
    name: "Seedlings to promote"
    filters:
      - 'status == "seedling"'
    order:
      - file.name
      - source
      - formula.days_old

  - type: table
    name: "Budding notes"
    filters:
      - 'status == "budding"'
    order:
      - file.name
      - formula.days_old

  - type: table
    name: "Evergreen"
    filters:
      - 'status == "evergreen"'
    order:
      - file.name
```

